          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23777854/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23777854/" class="">第132页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nietsche/" class=" " title="枯丙文">枯丙文</a>
                (一无所知)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23777854">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">世界不是由复杂的概念和事实构成，而只是人内心真实与直接的体验。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-09 22:48</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                世界不是由复杂的概念和事实构成，而只是人内心真实与直接的体验。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







